{"tid":1615060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家再畀多3秒睇睇，可以多個選擇","createTime":"2019-10-03T03:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T04:08:05.000Z","uid":95541,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"456c6e0e39a9ff48372eb44725f25c4337d607f5","tid":1615060,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"前線手足求你入嚟花3秒睇睇，可以改變全場革命<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614758</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打講得好好，事後文宣解釋係好重要。<br />\n宜家想畀多個選擇大家，就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事前預告</span><br />\n喺裝修行動前就發出警告，如果佢地冇公開道歉就首先進行不合作運動（罷睇唔買/攞件貨上手揸下）<br />\n然後就真係裝修。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗驚話咁做會加強警覺，佢警力就得咁多，仲要聽指揮官order，係絕對唔夠機動性。而我地的目標係極多（宿舍、狗屋、馬路、政府合署）<br />\n而且有危就有機，喺千軍萬馬中取敵將首級的震撼力絕對會大啲。<br />\n<br />\n利申：只提供方向，但係好想見到前線接納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a65a7552da67b74612b1234d3b35874bce22af","tid":1615060,"uid":93488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"549f93783802adfcb9cf87971927c0cec1f41176","tid":1615060,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"希望有人發現"},{"pid":"71bcb649f97d8949a0a5959022e714202fa52ad2","tid":1615060,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:33:03.000Z","msg":"[戰術] 大家必需善待黃店, 先有更多店敢黃!! 創造黃經濟圈!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aiGGatU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aiGGatU</a>"},{"pid":"3cadb50f146b0293aee86ad7edef093dd1ff2154","tid":1615060,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71bcb649f97d8949a0a5959022e714202fa52ad2","tid":1615060,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:33:03.000Z","msg":"[戰術] 大家必需善待黃店, 先有更多店敢黃!! 創造黃經濟圈!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aiGGatU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: